flexible continuation.} (12. e4 $5 {is an interesting alternative.} Nbd7 ({
of course, Black should not fall for} 12... Nxe4 $4 13. Bxg7 Kxg7 14. Nxe4 Bxe4
15. Qd4+ $18) 13. Qe2 e5 $5 {This is a typical way to limit white pieces.
Weakening of d5-square is not so relevant here because both white knights are
