Bc6 19. Nf1 Qb8 20. Ne3 Bb7 {0-1 (81) Van Wely,L (2667) -Caruana,F (2820) Wijk
aan Zee 2015 and now the right plan was} 21. Nf2 $1 Bc6 22. f4 $36) 14. Rfd1
Bh6 $132) 12... Nbd7 13. Rfd1 Rac8 {The most natural move.} ({Another
